Package: CKMRpop
Type: Package
Title: Forward-in-Time Simulation and Tabulation of Pairwise Relationships in Age-Structured Populations
Version: 0.1.1.999
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = c("Eric", "C."), "Anderson", , "eric.anderson@noaa.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1326-0840")
    )
  )
Description: Provides an R wrapper around the program spip, and a variety
    of functions to parse spip output to compile information about
    related pairs amongst sampled individuals.  Full documentation
    and vignettes are mirrored at https://eriqande.github.io/CKMRpop/index.html
    and can be read online there.
